snippet.title: Amber Heard Says She Doesn’t Label Her Sexuality | Access Hollywood
snippet.description:
"Justice League" star Amber Heard opened up to Allure about her choice not to define her sexuality and the Hollywood naysayers who warned her about making her love life public. For the full story, head over to http://www.allure.com/story/amber-heard-cover-story-december-2017
